sections.text:
38-2863.Temporary educational permit; fee.

The recipient of a temporary educational permit shall pay the required fee.

SourceLaws 1978, LB 675, § 14;Laws 1996, LB 1044, § 463;Laws 1999, LB 828, § 123;Laws 2003, LB 242, § 52;R.S.1943, (2003), § 71-1,147.30;Laws 2007, LB463, § 959.
